An '''apple orchard''' can be found immediately south-east of the [[Tree Gnome Stronghold]]. Inside the orchard, players can find a [[Rotten Apple Pile]]. During [[Mourning's End Part I]], players use a [[barrel]] on the pile to receive a [[rotten apples|barrel of rotten apples]], and then use the resulting barrel on the nearby [[Apple Press]] to make an [[apple barrel]].

The [[Scout (Tree Gnome Stronghold)|scout]] from [[The General's Shadow]] miniquest can also be found wandering just outside of the orchard, to the west.

Although the apple orchard was visible before Mourning's End Part I was released, it was inaccessible to players until then.

